WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:01.750
I've been doing a lot of videos back to

00:00:01.750 --> 00:00:01.760
back praying

00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:04.070
with y'all, but we

00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:05.830
have a lot of work to do

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:08.590
and I feel we make a lot of headway

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:10.070
together.

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:14.910
Many hands make light work. So,

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:21.590
you'll have to bear with me again.

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:23.270
All right, there's enough here.

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:25.430
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:28.350
for joining us again tonight. We're

00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:30.390
going to pray.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:32.030
I feel in my spirit we have great

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:33.190
victory

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:35.470
and I've been praying into it all day

00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:38.590
long. I am rejoicing,

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:42.390
believing that

00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:43.750
the things that happen in

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:45.710
Texas today are not going to happen

00:00:45.720 --> 00:00:48.070
anymore.

00:00:48.080 --> 00:00:50.990
I know what I've seen,

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:54.550
but I know what the word says concerning

00:00:54.560 --> 00:00:56.630
our protection and being in the right

00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:58.950
place at the right time.

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:00.830
Many of you may not know

00:01:04.160 --> 00:01:05.550
about

00:01:05.560 --> 00:01:07.550
the attack that happened today. If

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:09.990
you want to show them what happened

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:12.950
today, I'll go over some of the

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:16.190
things the Lord showed us last night

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:19.350
in prayer. A lot of that was about

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:22.350
tunnels underground

00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:25.870
and the military of Iran taking

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:28.750
what was in one area and putting it in

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:31.350
another area, making sure that what they

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:33.310
had was not going to be found by the

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:36.110
American troops or

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:38.190
by strikes,

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:41.910
trying to hide it deeper in the earth.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.710
Now, I thought that was interesting. It

00:01:43.720 --> 00:01:47.070
was

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:49.630
like a railroad under the earth,

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:53.110
underneath the soil of Iran with huge

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:55.030
caverns.

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:58.630
I could see train cars. That's

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:01.230
how big this was underground, like

00:02:01.240 --> 00:02:05.430
train cars that had military equipment

00:02:05.440 --> 00:02:08.029
and they were moving it from places that

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:10.950
were more vulnerable to places that

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:13.350
were more secure.

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:15.790
I could see them taking them closer

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.470
to

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:19.590
what would be

00:02:19.600 --> 00:02:22.870
the

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:25.350
Strait

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:28.070
of

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:28.710
Hormuz.

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:30.550
It was taking it towards what would be

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:31.670
Israel.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.790
They were going deeper

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:35.550
underground. I could see these men.

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:38.270
They had lights.

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.870
It looked like

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:41.510
smugglers.

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:43.310
As I was looking into

00:02:43.310 --> 00:02:43.320
that,

00:02:43.320 --> 00:02:44.870
we're going to pray into that tonight,

00:02:44.880 --> 00:02:48.390
even more so praying into an

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:51.230
uncovering and bringing them

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:53.190
to justice. They

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:54.830
were taking it towards

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:03.030
Iraq.

00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:07.030
These tunnels look like they were headed

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.750
towards the Iraq area. I

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:11.990
saw them moving like that. So they'd be

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:13.750
going west.

00:03:16.959 --> 00:03:20.310
We're going to pray

00:03:20.310 --> 00:03:20.320
that

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:21.790
they won't be able to

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:24.190
hide it. There's no place to hide.

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:26.830
There's no place to bury any biological

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:29.270
weapons or weapons of

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:31.270
mass destruction.

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:33.750
As I was seeing these payloads on

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:37.910
rockets,

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:40.030
they didn't have enough to put it on all

00:03:40.040 --> 00:03:42.390
of them, but there were certain ones

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:45.870
trying to figure out how to get past the

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:47.750
Iron Dome,

00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:51.830
being strategic in their strikes so that

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:54.190
they would send so many ahead.

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:56.870
Now, this is very strategic. What I'm

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:58.270
telling you, I saw by the spirit of God.

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:01.870
They would bombard it with a bunch of

00:04:01.880 --> 00:04:03.630
them at once.

00:04:04.800 --> 00:04:06.310
The Iron Dome and

00:04:06.320 --> 00:04:08.590
these defense systems, the Patriot or

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:10.630
whatever, would try to get the first

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:13.150
ones, but the one that they would miss

00:04:13.160 --> 00:04:17.550
would be the one lagging behind

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:19.349
and that was the one with the bad stuff

00:04:19.359 --> 00:04:21.349
on it.

00:04:21.359 --> 00:04:24.909
So it was so busy with the first

00:04:24.919 --> 00:04:28.190
that the one behind had the bad thing.

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:29.990
It missed this one because it was so

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.710
busy with the first ones.

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:34.390
So it shot in and it was able to hurt

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:36.990
people more. It was some kind of

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:47.870
chemical,

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:49.670
something. I don't know.

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:51.470
Y'all,

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:53.950
I only tell you what I see. I don't

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:57.110
know how to describe it. A lot

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:59.070
of times I'm doing the best I can with

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:00.590
the vision I have because I don't

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:02.670
understand all the military stuff.

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:04.750
But I'm going to tell you this was the

00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:07.830
same thing praying over Abraham

00:05:07.840 --> 00:05:10.830
Lincoln, praying over our servicemen and

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:14.110
women in our military bases.

00:05:14.120 --> 00:05:16.430
We see the bombardment of all the

00:05:16.440 --> 00:05:18.430
rockets. Braden showed me

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:21.590
they had 500 go off at one time.

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:23.550
It goes along with what the Lord was

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:25.790
showing me. Have they used those

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:27.870
special weapons? I don't believe they

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:29.110
have yet.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.670
I pray they haven't,

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:35.950
but it looks like stars falling,

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:38.070
just raining down like Christmas. It's

00:05:38.080 --> 00:05:39.710
bad.

00:05:39.720 --> 00:05:41.510
Have y'all seen that?

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:43.470
Can you show them that?

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:46.630
That is pretty

00:05:46.640 --> 00:05:52.030
substantial.

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:53.870
I can't even imagine living there

00:05:53.880 --> 00:05:55.990
and watching TV or whatever in your

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.710
living room and that going

00:05:58.720 --> 00:06:00.910
on outside and thinking it's

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:03.070
time to get out of here.

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:05.070
But

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:07.830
we pray for peace. We pray

00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:09.350
for them to

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:10.630
lay down their weapons and go on. You

00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:12.190
know, they're saying we have so

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:13.590
much more. If you kill one, we'll just

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:14.950
raise up another one right there

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:17.390
the next day to take the position. We

00:06:17.400 --> 00:06:19.110
don't care what you do. We're not giving

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:22.070
up. We'll keep bringing in new military.

00:06:22.070 --> 00:06:22.080
If

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:24.270
you eliminate that

00:06:24.280 --> 00:06:25.710
leader, we'll bring in another one the

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:27.070
next day.

00:06:27.080 --> 00:06:28.990
We're not going to give up what we

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:31.190
believe and all this stuff.

00:06:31.200 --> 00:06:33.590
It's really interesting. How far

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:35.110
will this go?

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:38.310
How far will this escalate?

00:06:38.320 --> 00:06:41.350
I'm waiting

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:44.150
for what I keep seeing concerning North

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:46.030
Korea

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:48.990
and Russia.

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:51.310
Will they get involved with

00:06:51.320 --> 00:06:53.390
this or will

00:06:53.400 --> 00:06:56.030
cool heads prevail?

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:58.630
I keep praying

00:06:58.640 --> 00:07:03.390
into what I keep seeing

00:07:03.400 --> 00:07:07.909
praying over Taiwan as the main target.

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:11.590
Praying over that island

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:13.550
for the Taiwan people, the

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:16.350
Taiwanese.

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:19.150
Praying over their allies with South

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.510
Korea, Japan,

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:24.270
Australia, praying for them to stand

00:07:24.280 --> 00:07:26.909
strong that they would have this glory

00:07:26.919 --> 00:07:29.190
dome around them that I keep seeing by

00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:31.190
the hand of God protecting these

00:07:31.200 --> 00:07:33.670
people. That China will have

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:36.270
a coup

00:07:36.280 --> 00:07:38.790
in their camp with their military and

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:41.270
with Xi, that there'll be a coup, some

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:43.550
kind of overthrowing, that there'll be so

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:45.190
much confusion that they'll turn on

00:07:45.200 --> 00:07:47.150
themselves.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:49.590
Kim Jong-un is another one that I

00:07:49.590 --> 00:07:49.600
truly

00:07:49.600 --> 00:07:51.950
believe we pray against any

00:07:51.960 --> 00:07:55.470
kind of retaliation from him.

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:57.910
I saw paranoia trying to come on his

00:07:57.920 --> 00:08:01.270
mind as he was worried because he sees

00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:03.350
how President Trump has

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.350
got

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:06.430
Venezuela, now he's

00:08:06.440 --> 00:08:08.030
next.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:09.710
I truly believe it's Cuba that's

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:11.470
next.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:14.150
I believe Cuba will be next after all

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:15.150
this.

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:19.990
How fast will this end? We're going

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:23.990
to pray tonight for divine protection

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:25.990
again over our troops, over our men and

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:28.230
women of service that are protecting our

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:31.790
homeland. God bless these

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:33.750
people that are risking their lives for

00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:34.909
us.

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:36.830
Some people agree with this, some people

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:40.149
don't. It seems to be split all over

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:42.430
social media. I see everybody.

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:44.390
You got people that are far left and far

00:08:44.400 --> 00:08:46.310
right that are mad. You got left people

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:48.710
that are happy and far right people

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.550
that are happy. This is really

00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:52.270
interesting because it's like a huge mixing

00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:54.430
pot.

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:56.390
Watching other nations,

00:08:56.400 --> 00:08:58.150
where is

00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:00.270
everybody with all this? Russia

00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:03.310
seems to be pretty upset about it.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.510
I don't know, as I keep

00:09:06.520 --> 00:09:08.390
praying into it,

00:09:08.400 --> 00:09:11.910
like I said, we don't pray the news.

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:13.230
If you're praying the news, you're

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:15.030
missing it.

00:09:15.040 --> 00:09:16.870
You must come up higher in your prayer

00:09:16.880 --> 00:09:17.950
life.

00:09:17.960 --> 00:09:20.350
An eagle doesn't

00:09:23.720 --> 00:09:25.910
fly with the crows.

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:28.550
It flies up high. I'm

00:09:28.550 --> 00:09:28.560
going

00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:31.829
to

00:09:31.829 --> 00:09:31.839
be

00:09:31.839 --> 00:09:34.990
an eagle. I'm

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:37.270
not a crow

00:09:37.280 --> 00:09:39.350
or a chicken.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:41.150
Chicken tastes good, but it ain't

00:09:41.160 --> 00:09:43.510
somebody I want to hang around.

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:47.070
You got to come up higher in what I'm

00:09:47.080 --> 00:09:48.310
trying to tell y'all in your prayer

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.430
life.

00:09:49.440 --> 00:09:52.270
It's not time to pray the news. We must

00:09:52.280 --> 00:09:54.910
see beyond the news.

00:09:54.920 --> 00:09:57.070
It's already too late.

00:10:04.160 --> 00:10:06.390
Russia President Putin says the

00:10:06.400 --> 00:10:09.030
assassination

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:11.230
of Iran's Supreme Leader is a brutal

00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:14.230
murder that violates ethics and

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:17.910
international law.

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:19.070
Wow.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.350
That's a pretty bold statement for

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:22.870
somebody who kills 20,000 people

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:25.910
a month

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:29.630
in Ukraine.

00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:31.670
I mean, wow. Calling the kettle black,

00:10:31.680 --> 00:10:35.430
huh?

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:37.790
I mean, that guy has no room to talk.

00:10:37.800 --> 00:10:40.030
He's murdered more people in the last

00:10:40.030 --> 00:10:40.040
two

00:10:40.040 --> 00:10:42.190
years than

00:10:42.190 --> 00:10:42.200
anyone;

00:10:42.200 --> 00:10:45.510
he's like a Hitler.

00:10:45.520 --> 00:10:46.950
But

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.790
with Ukraine and all that sadness that's

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:50.150
going on over there, the bloodshed that's

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:53.070
happening, it's terrible.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:55.430
So we're going to pray

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:57.790
over Hawaii.

00:10:57.800 --> 00:10:59.790
Now, I thought this was interesting, and

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:00.829
I'm not going to sit here and talk a

00:11:00.839 --> 00:11:02.870
long time because I don't want to keep

00:11:02.870 --> 00:11:02.880
y'all

00:11:02.880 --> 00:11:05.590
a long time tonight.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:07.790
I appreciate y'all being here so many

00:11:07.800 --> 00:11:09.230
nights in a row, and you've prayed with

00:11:09.240 --> 00:11:10.270
me.

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:14.070
We added up over six hours of prayer time

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:17.510
in the last couple of days of video, and

00:11:17.520 --> 00:11:19.390
a lot of you have watched all of it,

00:11:19.400 --> 00:11:21.829
praying with me, and so I want to honor

00:11:21.839 --> 00:11:24.590
your time. But okay, so

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:26.750
the blood moon tomorrow night. Is it

00:11:26.760 --> 00:11:27.910
tomorrow night?

00:11:27.910 --> 00:11:27.920
Yeah,

00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:30.430
the third. So it would be

00:11:30.440 --> 00:11:32.710
Monday night going

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:33.990
into Tuesday.

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.310
It's not Tuesday night going into

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:36.830
Wednesday because that's not the third. So

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:38.790
it's actually going to be

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:40.030
tomorrow night,

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:41.110
the blood moon.

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:42.870
Yeah, today's the first

00:11:42.870 --> 00:11:42.880
or

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:44.790
second... third. Yeah, let's see. So

00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:46.190
whatever it is, I believe it's probably

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:48.190
Tuesday. It might be Tuesday night.

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:50.030
That night going into...

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:51.910
well, it can't be Tuesday night

00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:53.750
going into that. It's Monday night going

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:56.070
into Tuesday.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:58.270
Has to be because it turns the

00:11:58.280 --> 00:11:59.550
next day;

00:11:59.560 --> 00:12:02.590
it's in the morning.

00:12:02.600 --> 00:12:06.310
So tomorrow night,

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:07.790
the total lunar eclipse of the blood moon

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:09.630
will be visible

00:12:09.640 --> 00:12:11.070
Tuesday night. Tomorrow

00:12:11.080 --> 00:12:12.670
night—well,

00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:15.430
today's Sunday.

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:16.790
So whatever,

00:12:16.800 --> 00:12:18.510
it's over

00:12:18.520 --> 00:12:20.390
Hawaii.

00:12:20.400 --> 00:12:23.870
The main totality is from the West Coast,

00:12:23.880 --> 00:12:25.430
where it's

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:27.470
visible, the big part like I'm talking

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:30.110
about where it's a full blood red moon.

00:12:30.120 --> 00:12:31.870
You know, there are phases,

00:12:31.880 --> 00:12:34.710
and the East Coast is not very much,

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:37.430
Central a little bit more, West Coast

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:39.150
full blood moon,

00:12:39.160 --> 00:12:42.590
Hawaii full blood moon big time,

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:46.190
South Korea, Taiwan full

00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:49.350
blood moon big time. Now Israel,

