incredible. If they're still here after

02:31:27.480 --> 02:31:28.510
that,

02:31:28.520 --> 02:31:31.990
7,000. So, 2,000 people

02:31:32.000 --> 02:31:33.310
left.

02:31:33.320 --> 02:31:35.990
Well, we love you. Remember, put a smile

02:31:36.000 --> 02:31:38.310
on your face and a song in your heart.

02:31:38.320 --> 02:31:39.790
Thank you for joining us. And we'll go

02:31:39.800 --> 02:31:42.310
over things we saw again

02:31:42.320 --> 02:31:45.270
today and tomorrow, and I'll tell

02:31:45.280 --> 02:31:47.230
you more of what I saw and bring it more

02:31:47.240 --> 02:31:48.910
to light.

02:31:48.920 --> 02:31:51.110
We appreciate you being here. God

02:31:51.120 --> 02:31:54.800
bless y'all. Love you. Bye-bye.

